    "body": "This is a major project and we are still in the design phase. Within two weeks we will publish a gRFC in https://github.com/grpc/proposal that describes our design and allows people to comment. The implementation will start after that.\r\n\r\nFor now I would suggest writing your own retry logic above our code. That is what several groups have done to use retries before we implement it"
